<p style="text-align: center;">As a Team Fox member, you’ll gain access to a handbook full of tips and tricks, a personalized fundraising page to collect donations and share word of your event and support from hundreds of other Team Fox fundraisers, just like you, all across the country!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Feeling inspired? Visit <a href="/admin/www.teamfox.org" class="orange">www.teamfox.org</a> to register, create an online fundraising page and get started today!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Have a question? Need some advice? Our team is here to help! Email <a href="mailto:teamfox@michaeljfox.org" class="orange">TeamFox@michaeljfox.org</a> for more info.</p>
